text: Couple-ish is a Canadian LGBTQ+ web series starring Kaitlyn Alexander, Mercedes Morris, Sharon Belle and Nicholas Potter. The series follows Dee Warson, a non-binary illustrator, who becomes entangled in the lie that they are in a common law partnership with their roommate, Rachel Mannt. The series premiered on December 9, 2015 and concluded the first season on March 9, 2016.
